### Koa v2 Instrumentation (Node.js)

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

This entry highlights the addition of `@newrelic/koa` as a dependency, enabling first-party instrumentation for Koa v2.0.0 and higher. This allows for independent installation and usage of Koa instrumentation within the New Relic Node.js agent, providing performance monitoring for Koa-based applications.

```bash
npm install @newrelic/koa --save
